<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Verify your CSI-CTF account</title>
</head>

<body style="width: 100%; overflow-x: hidden;">

    <div style="width: 600px;
        color: white;
        max-width:80%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        border: 2px solid #45619e;
        line-height: 1.3em;
        background-image:radial-gradient(13em circle at 100% 100%,rgb(171, 185, 214),#597edc)">

        <div style="height: 6vh; background-color: #003399;"></div>

        <div>
            <hr
                style="background: linear-gradient( to right, rgba(0, 51, 153, 1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 23%, rgba(0, 51, 153, 1) 100% ); height: 3px; margin: 0; border: 0;">
        </div>

        <div style="padding-left: 20px; padding-right:20px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom:10px;">

            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 15px;">

                <img src="https://static.csivit.com/ctf/logo.png" alt="" style="width: 75%;">

            </div>
            <h1 style="text-align: center; line-height: 30px; font-size: 1.5em; color: white;">Verify your CSI-CTF Account</h1>
            <hr style="background-image:linear-gradient( to right, #597edc 0%, rgb(171, 185, 214) 25%, #597edc 100% ); height: 2px;
     border:none;">
            <br style="height: 15px;">
            <p>
                <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: white;">Greetings from CSI-VIT!</span><br>

                <div style="font-size: 15px; color: white;">Thank you, {{name}}!<br><br></div>

                <div style="font-size: 15px; color: white;">You have successfully registered for <span
                        style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">CSI-CTF</span>!
                    To verify your email, click <a href="{{vLink}}" style="color:rgb(255, 224, 87)">here</a>.</div><br>

                <div style="font-size: 13px; color: white;">
                    <span style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">If the above link does not work, copy and paste the following link:</span>
                    <br>
                    <a href="{{vLink}}"
                        style="color:rgb(255, 224, 87); text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; word-wrap: break-word">{{vLink}}</a>
                </div>
                <br>

                <div style="font-size: 13px; color: white;">If it wasn't you, you can ignore this email. </div><br>
                <div style="font-size: 15px; color: white;">Stay tuned for further updates. <br>Happy Hacking!</div><br>
                <div style="color: white;">Regards,<br>CSI-VIT</div><br>

            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <hr
                style="background: linear-gradient( to right, rgba(0, 51, 153, 1) 0%, rgba(249, 145, 0, 1) 23%, rgba(0, 51, 153, 1) 100% ); height: 3px; margin: 0; border: 0;">
        </div>

        <div
            style=" background-color: #003399; padding-top:20px; padding-left:20px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
            <div style="padding-top: 5px;float:left;">
                <a href="https://instagram.com/csivitu/">
                    <img style="width: 20px; padding-right:10px;"
                        src="https://i.imgur.com/m9yaDUZ.png">
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/csivitu/">
                    <img style="width: 20px; padding-right:10px;"
                        src="https://i.imgur.com/oJ19aMv.png">
                </a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/csivitu/">
                    <img style="width: 20px;"
                        src="https://i.imgur.com/zxE67NG.png">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div style="float: right;">
                <img style="width: 150px; height:32px;"
                    src="https://i.imgur.com/AuQJ23N.png">
            </div>

            <div style="clear: both;"></div>

        </div>
        </div>
</body>

</html>
